data.description: Open concept ranch waiting for its new owner to complete projects and add finishing touches. This 5 bedroom 2 bath ranch in the Village of Howards Grove has a lot to offer. Possible 6th bedroom (or office) in the finished  lower level. 3 egress windows have recently been added to create 2+ additional bedrooms along w/ a family rm. Main level has a true open concept floor plan with vaulted ceilings perfect for gatherings. Patio doors to deck, gas FP, partially fenced yard, 2.5 car drywalled garage w/ counter & cupboards, all new windows throughout except for 2, Basement is stubbed for bathroom, new water heater. New flooring in both bathrooms and laundry area.
